column5: Will be heading through Fort Frances around 6:30am this Friday. Any stores open at that time for some last minute food supplies and beer/booze. Just need a good store and the hours they are open. Thanks

There is a "Safeway" ( I think) grocery store that will be open on the 11 heading east from the border crossing. The Provincial liquor and beer stores ( separate stores several blocks apart) do not open until 9:00 a.m. I believe. -JBP
Safeway opens at 0600 am on the weekends Fri -Sun and the beer and liquor stores open at 0930am
